    "description": "qc3C - reference-free quality control for Hi-C DNA sequencing libraries.\n\nThe primary aim of qc3C is to infer the proportion of \"signal\" within a Hi-C sequencing library and thereby provide a means of quality control. A big advantange of qc3C is that this can be done without access to a reference sequence, which until now has been a significant stopping point for projects not involving model organisms.",
